{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"@MoonDevOnYT this user on x has youtube videos too. has some interesting insights on how to automate and similar stuff. one of his latest video has bot doing under 20 bets and farming good percentage witha  edge on crypto markets, lemme try to find transriptions if i can but start exploring his stuff\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Excellent find. Let's deep-dive into **@MoonDevOnYT**'s methodology. This could save us weeks of trial-and-error.\\n\\nI'll start researching his content to understand:\\n- His specific edge on 5/15min crypto markets\\n- Technical architecture he uses\\n- What data sources he leverages\\n- How he connects wallet/automates trades\\n- Performance metrics\\n\\nLet me search for his content:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"local_web_search\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260319_235951_d6733e.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.935539"}
