{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"1. Do you have a Polygon wallet with USDC? (wallet address + amount) i dont have one yet but i can set it up and give you like 300-400 cad thats all i have right now                                               \\r   2. Are you willing to use a **separate** wallet for bot trading? (not main wallet) sure                                 \\r   3. Do you have access to a VPS or machine that can run 24/7? (or use your Macbook) we can use this same vps that im running you on.                             \"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Excellent answers. Let's clarify and lock in the setup:\\n\\n## Confirmed Requirements\\n\\n\\u2705 **Separate wallet** for bot trading  \\n\\u2705 **VPS**: Use this same server (24/7 available)  \\n\\u2705 **Manual trading experience**: You know the mechanics  \\n\\u2705 **Capital**: $300-400 CAD (~$210-280 USD) for testing  \\n\\u26a0\\ufe0f **Binance data**: You said \\\"i dont want it but i was gonna give it for you for the most recent data\\\" \\u2014 **Binance API is FREE** (no cost). We absolutely want it for the fastest price feed. I'll set up a Bina\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260319_235951_d6733e.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.935697"}
