{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"make prompts for things you would like to research and things you would like more context about and stuff like that plan very extensive and detailed research and then i will make my gemini research all of that i can add files too in research so make prompts for everything you would like to extensively research and get information on and i will put my gemini deep reserach to worka and make a files with context to attach to it on what were trying to do and what we actually know and stuff like that\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Excellent idea. Let's create a **comprehensive research package** that we'll send to Gemini (and Grok agents) to gather all the edge information we need.\\n\\nI'll create three main files:\\n\\n1. **`RESEARCH_CONTEXT.md`** - Explains our mission, what we know, what we need\\n2. **`RESEARCH_PROMPTS.md`** - All the detailed research questions for Gemini (categorized)\\n3. **`GROK_ALPHA_PROMPTS.md`** - Prompts for Grok agents to scrape X/Twitter for real-time alpha\\n\\nLet's build these now:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"write_file\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260319_235951_d6733e.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.935924"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"also research for the development part too after that if you want to and then list down all the todo tasks for me and all the todo tasks for you. so i know where were at and give me progress update on what the plan and how will we move forward and what are all the steps and all that good stuff make couple of files and push that to git too so i can read em\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Perfect. I'll create a **complete research and development package** with all prompts, tasks, and progress tracking. Let me build these files now:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"write_file\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260319_235951_d6733e.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.935949"}
