{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Thielon, thanks for the full debug report + retry fix. Root cause clear.\\rNow let's make smarter long-term changes based on my ideas:\\r\\rSummarization frequency\\rWhat is this session_search summarization actually for? We just need the agent to keep learning. Is it mainly for Telegram chat history? If yes, let\\u2019s drop it from every-30-min crons and run it only 2x/day (e.g. 9am and 9pm). Can you decouple/throttle it so it doesn\\u2019t burn auxiliary quota every time any cron calls session_search?\\rSeparate m\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Let me map the full picture before designing the fix.\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}, {\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}, {\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260318_203625_1b5883.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.936941"}
