{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Main chat + coding/dev key \\u2192 Hunter Alpha (openrouter/hunter-alpha)\\rDaily Hermes brain + planning + long chats. Switch to Nemotron 3 Super (nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b:free) when you\\u2019re deep in coding sprints or multi-agent builds (faster + more efficient).\\rPro move for Hermes:\\r\\rRoute vision steps to Healer\\rRoute planning/coding to Hunter or Nemotron\\rLet the agent decide via tool calls (Hermes already supports model routing).\\r\\rAll three are live and free right now \\u2014 plug the strings straig\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Got it \\u2014 smart model routing. Let me wire it all up.\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"patch\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260318_203625_1b5883.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.937011"}
