{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"1. **Create GitHub org** `thielon-llc` and transfer any repos you want there. Idea factory will use it.\\r   2. **Tune scoring** weights in `orchestrator.py` if you want different priority.\\r   3. **Extend code generation** in `dev-agent.py` to produce more sophisticated templates (DB, auth, etc.).\\r   4. **Add more deployment targets** (Vercel frontend, Fly.io) in `deploy-agent.py`.\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_184504_ffbd29.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.939724"}
