{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"also how i want you to automate this is you have secrets and ideas and al the learnings and insights going on all day. build on those ideas and make projects on it and around it and ask it to deploy and develop that all the time. make a engine that takes ideas and information in formats them make some agents and skills that make those ideas into a project formation and plan. and then subagents and skills for design and architecture-planning and design and development and testing and deployment a\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"# IDEA-TO-DEPLOYMENT ENGINE \\u2014 DESIGN\\n\\nYou\\u2019ve just described **Autonomous Infinite Factory**. Let me build it right now.\\n\\n## Architecture\\n\\n```\\nIdea Engine (runs every 30 min)\\n\\u251c\\u2500\\u2500 IdeaIngestor (scrapes Obsidian, Moltbook feed, Polymarket alerts, manual queue)\\n\\u251c\\u2500\\u2500 IdeaScorer (Thielon contrarian/monopoly metrics \\u2192 priority queue)\\n\\u2514\\u2500\\u2500 ProjectPlanner (creates spec, architecture, compliance checklist)\\n\\nIf score > threshold \\u2192 spawns:\\n\\u251c\\u2500\\u2500 DesignAgent (Figma-like mockups + design system)\\n\\u251c\\u2500\\u2500 ArchitectureA\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_183815_b84825.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942186"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"also how i want you to automate this is you have secrets and ideas and al the learnings and insights going on all day. build on those ideas and make projects on it and around it and ask it to deploy and develop that all the time. make a engine that takes ideas and information in formats them make some agents and skills that make those ideas into a project formation and plan. and then subagents and skills for design and architecture-planning and design and development and testing and deployment a\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_183815_b84825.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942207"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Review the conversation above and consider saving or updating a skill if appropriate.\\n\\nFocus on: was a non-trivial approach used to complete a task that required trial and error, or changing course due to experiential findings along the way, or did the user expect or desire a different method or outcome?\\n\\nIf a relevant skill already exists, update it with what you learned. Otherwise, create a new skill if the approach is reusable.\\nIf nothing is worth saving, just say 'Nothing to save.' and stop.\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"session_search\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_183815_b84825.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942225"}
