{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"get the new browser use from git. v2 is crazy people are saying also can i download chrome in here. if we can please do it and show me how to use it. and i want you to be able touse it in the new update theyve made access for agents to use the web\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"I'll investigate the new browser automation tools, check if Chrome can be installed, and set it up for agent use. Let me start by searching for the latest developments.\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"web_search\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942264"}
