{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"i want to use my google account in chromium or i have one email for thielon too if that helps. you can set that up in the chromium or if you are comgy without it were good there too.\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Great idea! Using a persistent Google account in Chromium gives your agent:\\n- Persistent login state (no re-authentication)\\n- Access to personalized data (Gmail, Drive, Search history)\\n- Browser extensions\\n- Cookies and local storage\\n- More human-like fingerprint\\n\\nLet's set up a dedicated THIELON Chromium profile with your Google account. This will be a **separate browser profile** just for your agent.\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942303"}
