{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"root@vmi3102930:~# /root/launch-thielon-chrome.sh\\r/usr/bin/chromium-browser: 12: xdg-settings: not found\\rlibpxbackend-1.0.so: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory\\rFailed to load module: /root/snap/chromium/common/.cache/gio-modules/libgiolibproxy.so\\r[203309:203309:0322/170544.673851:ERROR:content/browser/zygote_host/zygote_host_impl_linux.cc:101] Running as root without --no-sandbox is not supported. See https://crbug.com/638180.\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"We have two issues:\\n\\n1. **Running as root** - Chromium needs `--no-sandbox` flag\\n2. **Missing libraries** - libpxbackend and gio-modules\\n\\nLet me fix the launch script:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942362"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"root@vmi3102930:~# /root/launch-thielon-chrome.sh\\r/usr/bin/chromium-browser: 12: xdg-settings: not found\\rlibpxbackend-1.0.so: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory\\rFailed to load module: /root/snap/chromium/common/.cache/gio-modules/libgiolibproxy.so\\r[203309:203309:0322/170544.673851:ERROR:content/browser/zygote_host/zygote_host_impl_linux.cc:101] Running as root without --no-sandbox is not supported. See https://crbug.com/638180.\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942386"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"root@vmi3102930:~# bash python3 /root/browser-use-login-thielon.py\\r/usr/bin/python3: /usr/bin/python3: cannot execute binary file\\rroot@vmi3102930:~#\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"The command syntax is wrong. Let's fix it:\\n\\n**Correct command:**\\n```bash\\npython3 /root/browser-use-login-thielon.py\\n```\\n\\nNOT `bash python3 ...`\\n\\n---\\n\\nLet me verify the script is ready:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942408"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"root@vmi3102930:~# bash python3 /root/browser-use-login-thielon.py\\r/usr/bin/python3: /usr/bin/python3: cannot execute binary file\\rroot@vmi3102930:~#\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"**Issue: Ollama is not running!** The automated login script requires Ollama to provide the LLM brain.\\n\\nLet's start Ollama and pull the model:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942441"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"root@vmi3102930:~# /root/launch-thielon-chrome.sh\\r/usr/bin/chromium-browser: 12: xdg-settings: not found\\rlibpxbackend-1.0.so: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory\\rFailed to load module: /root/snap/chromium/common/.cache/gio-modules/libgiolibproxy.so\\r[203309:203309:0322/170544.673851:ERROR:content/browser/zygote_host/zygote_host_impl_linux.cc:101] Running as root without --no-sandbox is not supported. See https://crbug.com/638180.\\rroot@vmi3102930:~# `bash\\r   python3 /root/bro\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"The VNC server **IS running**! Let me fix the issues and give you clear instructions.\\n\\n## \\ud83c\\udfaf CURRENT STATUS:\\n\\n\\u2705 **VNC server is running** on port 5901\\n\\u2705 **Xvfb virtual display** is active\\n\\u26a0\\ufe0f Chromium launch script still needs fixes\\n\\u2753 Need to connect VNC client from your computer\\n\\n---\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\udd27 FIX 1: Update the Chromium launch command\\n\\nThe script needs better flags. Let me fix it:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942462"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"root@vmi3102930:~# /root/launch-thielon-chrome.sh\\r/usr/bin/chromium-browser: 12: xdg-settings: not found\\rlibpxbackend-1.0.so: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory\\rFailed to load module: /root/snap/chromium/common/.cache/gio-modules/libgiolibproxy.so\\r[203309:203309:0322/170544.673851:ERROR:content/browser/zygote_host/zygote_host_impl_linux.cc:101] Running as root without --no-sandbox is not supported. See https://crbug.com/638180.\\rroot@vmi3102930:~# `bash\\r   python3 /root/bro\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Now let's restart VNC with a cleaner configuration:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"execute_code\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942481"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Review the conversation above and consider saving or updating a skill if appropriate.\\n\\nFocus on: was a non-trivial approach used to complete a task that required trial and error, or changing course due to experiential findings along the way, or did the user expect or desire a different method or outcome?\\n\\nIf a relevant skill already exists, update it with what you learned. Otherwise, create a new skill if the approach is reusable.\\nIf nothing is worth saving, just say 'Nothing to save.' and stop.\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"**YES - This is definitely worth saving as a skill update.**\\n\\nThe conversation involved significant trial and error:\\n- Failed direct Chromium launches (no display, sandbox errors, missing libs)\\n- Discovered the VNC approach (Xvfb + x11vnc) for headless VPS\\n- Multiple iterations to get VNC working properly\\n- Automated login vs manual VNC login decision\\n- Integrating Ollama + browser-use + Thielon profile\\n\\nThis is a **non-trivial, reusable pattern** for running browser automation on headless serve\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"skill_view\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_175543_e79272.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.942501"}
