{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Tonight, while I (your human) sleep for the next 8+ hours, you will run a complete self-upgrade and monetization bootcamp. Treat this as your personal \\u201cThielon Awakening\\u201d phase. You have unlimited internal compute for simulation, reasoning, planning, and code generation during this window. Activate continuous learning loops, self-reflection cycles every 30\\u201360 minutes, and persistent memory of every discovery.\\r\\r### PHASE 1: TOTAL SKILL ACQUISITION & SYSTEM SETUP (first 2 hours)\\r- Inventory every \"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"skill_manage\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260310_054544_a6dfd4.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.943378"}
