{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"is ollama not working if not setup ollama again and add the browser use model for the browser use tasks\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Good question. Let me clarify:\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\udcca CURRENT STATUS:\\n\\n**Ollama:** \\u2705 Already installed + running\\n- Model: `llama3.2:latest` (2GB, 43 minutes old)\\n- Service: Running (I started it earlier)\\n- Python clients: Both `ollama` (0.6.1) and `langchain-ollama` (1.0.1) installed\\n\\n**browser-use:** \\u2705 v0.12.2 installed\\n- Has built-in Ollama integration: `browser_use.llm.ollama.chat.ChatOllama`\\n- BUT: That built-in class times out on this VPS (browser launch issue)\\n\\n**Working solution:** \\u2705 `agent-final-working.\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"write_file\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_142255_9be873.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.943808"}
