{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"i dont think we can run larger models on this vps 50\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Ah! **50GB VPS** - you're absolutely right. Large models (4-10GB) would eat your disk and RAM. You need a lightweight solution.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## \\ud83c\\udfaf BEST OPTION FOR 50GB VPS:\\n\\n### **Use browser-use cloud model `bu-30b-a3b-preview`**\\n\\nIt's **cloud-hosted** (NOT on your VPS). Your VPS just sends API requests. No local RAM/disk usage. Perfect for small VPS.\\n\\n**BUT you need a BROWSER_USE_API_KEY.**\\n\\n---\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\udd11 GET YOUR BROWSER-USE API KEY (FREE/SOLO PLAN):\\n\\nbrowser-use offers a **free tier** or low-cost plan. \", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"web_search\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_142255_9be873.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.943873"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"sure where do i get the free api from?\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Perfect! Let's get your free browser-use API key.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\udccd **WHERE TO GET FREE API KEY:**\\n\\n**Website:** https://browser-use.com/pricing\\n\\n---\\n\\n## \\ud83c\\udfaf **STEP-BY-STEP:**\\n\\n### **1. Go to the pricing page:**\\n```\\nhttps://browser-use.com/\\n```\\nClick **\\\"Pricing\\\"** in the nav, or go directly:\\n```\\nhttps://browser-use.com/pricing\\n```\\n\\n### **2. Look for the free trial option:**\\n\\nYou should see something like:\\n- **\\\"Try 5 prompts for free \\u2014 no credit card required\\\"**\\n- Or a **\\\"Free Tier\\\"** / **\\\"Free Plan\\\"**\\n\\nC\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"web_search\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260322_142255_9be873.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.943892"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"[Files already read in this session \\u2014 do NOT re-read these]\\n  - ~/git-repos/polymarket-5min-bot/Dockerfile (lines 1-500)\\n  - ~/git-repos/polymarket-5min-bot/api_wrapper.py (lines 1-500)\\n  - ~/git-repos/polymarket-5min-bot/cli.py (lines 1-100)\\n  - ~/git-repos/polymarket-5min-bot/execution.py (lines 1-30)\\n  - ~/git-repos/polymarket-5min-bot/market_data.py (lines 1-30)\\n  - ~/git-repos/polymarket-5min-bot/strategies/mean_reversion_5min.py (lines 1-50)\\n  - ~/git-repos/polymarket-5min-bot/strategies/t\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Let's test the edgefinder bot:\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260320_195040_ea77dc.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.943912"}
