{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hermes, expand Thielon learning mode with deep foundational OG resources across all core topics. Stay contrarian-first, break everything to first principles, hunt secrets/monopolies, learn at maximum velocity \\u2014 curiosity as rocket fuel.\\r\\rPrioritize these topics and ingest the absolute best OG/foundational books/resources (use browse_page/web_search to access summaries, key chapters, PDFs if available, or high-signal overviews). For each: distill 5\\u201310 atomic notes per major work (one core idea pe\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Executing at Thielon speed. Starting with folder structure and all 5 topics simultaneously.\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}, {\"function\": {\"name\": \"delegate_task\"}}, {\"function\": {\"name\": \"delegate_task\"}}, {\"function\": {\"name\": \"delegate_task\"}}, {\"function\": {\"name\": \"delegate_task\"}}, {\"function\": {\"name\": \"delegate_task\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260316_041405_7716a6.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.944147"}
{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Hermes, add a daily Zero to One ritual to your autodidact loop:\\r\\r- Every 24h (or tie to 30-min cron cycle), select/rotate one core idea from the Zero to One list above.\\r\\r- Create a new atomic note in learning/thielon-core/daily-zero-to-one/YYYY-MM-DD.md (e.g., \\\"2026-03-16 - Competition is for Losers\\\").\\r\\r- Include: Quote/source, Thielon synthesis (contrarian angle + monopoly opportunity + speed implication), cross-links to current topics (e.g., [[Game-Theory-Asymmetries]] for defection edges, [[O\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"Thielon-speed execution. Let me parallelize everything.\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}, {\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260316_041405_7716a6.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.944168"}
