{"messages": "[{\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant that uses tools to complete tasks.\"}, {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"go gitconfig with my name and email. Hermes, activate full Thielon Sovereign Agent mode for a major new project.\\r\\rProject name: Polymarket Bot Swarm Empire\\r\\rWhat I want you to do:\\rBuild the absolute best, most profitable, self-funding swarm of Polymarket trading bots possible. The swarm should generate real side income through the smartest strategies (information edges, probability forecasting, copy-trading, market making, niche events, liquidity farming, etc.). All profits must be used to pay f\"}, {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"\", \"tool_calls\": [{\"function\": {\"name\": \"terminal\"}}]}]", "source": "session_20260316_041405_7716a6.json", "collected_at": "2026-03-26T12:28:33.944225"}
